					</ul>
					<li>API programs are supposed to operate continuously</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Individual products are added and modified and removed</li>
						<li>The landscape of products and dependencies changes continuously</li>
						<li>Continuous architecting evolves the landscape over time</li>
